{
  "schemaVersion": 1,
  "id": "寻狗_梦待死之礼",
  "entry": "root",
  "meta": {
    "title": "寻狗Demo·梦·待死之礼（①.5 全游戏的眼）"
  },
  "nodes": {
    "root": {
      "type": "switch",
      "cases": [
        {
          "conditions": [
            {
              "narrative": "scenario_梦待死之礼",
              "state": "woken",
              "reached": true
            }
          ],
          "next": "done_1"
        }
      ],
      "defaultNext": "n1"
    },
    "done_1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "那一觉的事，他谁也没说过。",
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "n1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "深潭那口冷水，差点把他带走。等那股劲把他从水底拽上岸，他已经分不清是死是活——趴在泥里，冷、呛、乏，眼皮一合，人就沉了底。",
      "next": "n2"
    },
    "n2": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "一条夜路。雾薄。远处一户人家亮着灯，暖黄暖黄的，是这片黑里唯一的光。",
      "next": "n3"
    },
    "n3": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "（脚自己在往那边走。路两旁啥子都没得。静得只剩我自己的脚步声。）",
      "next": "n_house",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "empty_eyes"
      }
    },
    "n_house": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_梦待死之礼",
            "signal": "meng_house"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "n4"
    },
    "n4": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "门在他敲之前就开了。一对老两口站在门里，灯光从他们背后涌出来。",
      "next": "n5"
    },
    "n5": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "sceneNpc",
        "npcId": "npc_dream_old_woman"
      },
      "text": "「可算回来了。」",
      "next": "n6",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "n6": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "不问姓名。笑得很真。屋里桌上饭已经摆好——一碗白米饭，还冒着热气。像今晚刚摆的，又像等了他很久。",
      "next": "n7"
    },
    "n7": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "那碗饭，一双筷子，直直插在饭中央。",
      "next": "n8"
    },
    "n8": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "（饿。饿得前胸贴后背。老两口在旁边看着他，和善地，等。）",
      "next": "n_eat",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "empty_eyes"
      }
    },
    "n_eat": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "chooseAction",
          "params": {
            "prompt": "",
            "allowCancel": false,
            "options": [
              {
                "text": "【吃】",
                "actions": [
                  {
                    "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
                    "params": {
                      "sourceType": "dialogue",
                      "sourceId": "寻狗_梦待死之礼",
                      "signal": "meng_ate"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "n9"
    },
    "n9": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "他吃得很急。老妇人不声不响给他添了一回。没人说话。灯影暖暖的。",
      "next": "n10"
    },
    "n10": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "饭罢，老妇人捧来一身干净衣裳——浆洗得发白的棉布，针脚还新，线头都没剪。",
      "next": "n11"
    },
    "n11": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "他摸了半天，没摸到一颗扣子。全是结带的。",
      "next": "n12"
    },
    "n12": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "（……样式真旧。）",
      "next": "n_clothed",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "n_clothed": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_梦待死之礼",
            "signal": "meng_clothed"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "n13"
    },
    "n13": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "穿上了。很合身。像照着他的身量缝的。",
      "next": "n14"
    },
    "n14": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "老头把他引到里屋。让他睡的不是床——是一块卸下来的门板，脚朝着门口。脚边点着一盏豆大的灯。",
      "next": "n15"
    },
    "n15": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "院里有人在烧纸。火光透窗，一明一灭。",
      "next": "n16"
    },
    "n16": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "sceneNpc",
        "npcId": "npc_dream_old_man"
      },
      "text": "（轻声）「给你烧的。」",
      "next": "n17",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "empty_eyes"
      }
    },
    "n17": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "关二狗躺下。吃饱了，穿暖了，困意压上来。——他这辈子，没被这么好好待过。",
      "next": "n_lying"
    },
    "n_lying": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_梦待死之礼",
            "signal": "meng_lying"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "n18"
    },
    "n18": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "院门外"
      },
      "text": "（一个拖长的调子，远远传来）「回来咯——」",
      "next": "n19"
    },
    "n19": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "屋里一家人"
      },
      "text": "（围在门板边，齐声、轻轻地，替他应）「回来了。」",
      "next": "n20"
    },
    "n20": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "老妇人俯下身，像哄孩子入睡一样，把一方白纸，轻轻盖上他的脸。",
      "next": "n21"
    },
    "n21": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "纸随他的呼吸，一起，一伏。一起，一伏。",
      "next": "n22"
    },
    "n22": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "然后，不动了。",
      "next": "n_stop"
    },
    "n_stop": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_梦待死之礼",
            "signal": "meng_paper_stopped"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "waitMs",
          "params": {
            "durationMs": 1600
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "n_tune"
    },
    "n_tune": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_梦待死之礼",
            "signal": "meng_tune"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "n23"
    },
    "n23": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "极远处，飘来半句跑了调的小调。",
      "next": "n24"
    },
    "n24": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "纸——猛地，一颤。",
      "next": "n_gap"
    },
    "n_gap": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "waitMs",
          "params": {
            "durationMs": 900
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "n25"
    },
    "n25": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "—— 两 天 后 ——",
      "next": "n26"
    },
    "n26": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "大晴天。鸟叫。城外土路上，牛车碾过辙印。关二狗坐在路边石头上：头发乱成鸡窝，眼下两团青黑。他盯着地上一只蚂蚁，看了很久，很久。",
      "next": "n27"
    },
    "n27": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "……好饿。",
      "next": "n28",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "empty_eyes"
      }
    },
    "n28": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "他站起来，拍拍屁股，往城里走。身上还是自己那身破衣裳——梦里的东西，一件都没跟出来。除了饿。",
      "next": "n_wake"
    },
    "n_wake": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_梦待死之礼",
            "signal": "meng_woken"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "fadeWorldFromBlack",
          "params": {
            "durationMs": 1200
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "end1": {
      "type": "end"
    }
  }
}
